select "ONLINE RECRUITMENT SYSTEM"; then do not enter any search 
criteria, but click the grey search button. You will then be able to 
scroll down to the job. If you have any queries about applying on the 
online system, please email <a href="mailto:hr.jobs@lse.ac.uk" rel="email">hr.jobs@lse.ac.uk</a> 
or call 020 7107 5242, quoting reference 1202529. Three letters of 
reference and one writing sample should also be sent directly to 
<a href="mailto:philosophy-dept@LSE.ac.uk" rel="email">philosophy-dept@LSE.ac.uk</a>. 
Please see the 'How to Apply' document for more details. The closing 
date for receipt of applications is 31 October 2011 (11:59 p.m. UK time). 
Regrettably, we are unable to accept any late applications. We value 
diversity and wish to promote equality at all levels.
